{"tid":2307663,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[交易心理] 建立Trade plan的目的和重要性","createTime":"2020-12-01T10:07:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-01T13:52:57.000Z","uid":43407,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bd85a2038c1fbb7bd3103318ed76d1fe37ce51fd","tid":2307663,"uid":43407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:07:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1858365591112043/photos/a.2812094215739171/2821144561500803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1858365591112043%2Fphotos%2Fa.2812094215739171%2F2821144561500803&d=3wrM%2FJom4zLweqSprMIx0vUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=33e0e6f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1858365591112043/photos/a.2812094215739171/2821144561500803</a><br />\n<br />\n幾天前和各Heads of Dealing desk分享一個小米集團的港股個股Trade plan，有位朋友留言問，個buy order flow zone距離現價有一段相當距離，價位真的會重回這個zone嗎？這個問題令我想和大家重新探討一下何謂一個trade plan和應該如何看待它。<br />\n<br />\n首先，回答這位朋友的疑問，當然我地無辦法預知價位會否重回到這個zone，這並不是我們制定trade plan的重點。重點是，若果價位真的重回這個buy order flow zone，我們就執行這個trade plan。假設三個月後價位終於回到zone內，即是三個月前，我們已經設定好入市價位，止蝕位置，甚至止賺位（如果用回報風險比率的止賺方法），這亦是Order Flow Theory的可貴之處。那若果價格繼續上升，沒有回調到這個buy zone，那會怎樣？那我們便甚麼都不做，等待其他setup，不會有任何損失。這就是一個完整的trade plan，是一個IF.....THEN.....ELSE.....的process。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cBSv94X.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcBSv94X.png&h=39c4f2c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我每天和大家分析恆指美指等走勢都一樣，會做很多projection，即是一些假設，若果急速突破造出新的order flow zone，我們便等待價格重回zone內入市，若果價格沒做到我們的要求，我們便繼續耐心等待。這就是一個IF.....THEN.....ELSE.....process，一個完整的trade plan。<br />\n<br />\n每天我地打開圖表看市場，都應該如我以上所講，去建立自己的trade plan，若果我見到XXX我才入市，不然的話就甚麼都不做。能夠養成這個習慣，便不會（或者無咁容易）被價格變動引致情緒主導的交易操作。希望在過去的一段日子，我能為各位灌輸這個mindset，對建立長期的交易穩定性，必會有相當大幫助。"},{"pid":"f3b318ca89ad0ae1d766e209a25c1491a6177ce8","tid":2307663,"uid":3055,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:08:25.000Z","msg":"衝呀頭位支持塵sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c25983fdec5c8bc345975a56e06de43efa727b3","tid":2307663,"uid":56558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:08:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd685be4b4c3fff3350087928e8b39dd97908471","tid":2307663,"uid":139173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:09:25.000Z","msg":"Lm<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87401197542d8d406781eb083bd44fa2f874a555","tid":2307663,"uid":29878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:10:03.000Z","msg":"LM <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d19f5e093a46a871f52521aac9a1ab9407fa4d","tid":2307663,"uid":85803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:10:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8659a936347239a537aaf156cd9ed7f33aaf61a2","tid":2307663,"uid":323694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9fd6a2c7e51bee76b57fcfc0ee74f50146c162e","tid":2307663,"uid":43816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:13:16.000Z","msg":"要好好建立心態<br />\n唔到價就寧願唔做<br />\n造唔到order flow zone就繼續食花生"},{"pid":"7590059a48b5f54b8fd84d874cb077c8d2cf285e","tid":2307663,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:16:28.000Z","msg":"lmmmm"},{"pid":"9babbc732eefdbf5c4f574c765ccc8f803031581","tid":2307663,"uid":72304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d9fd6a2c7e51bee76b57fcfc0ee74f50146c162e","tid":2307663,"uid":43816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-01T10:13:16.000Z","msg":"要好好建立心態<